<h3>Directions to the Centre</h3>

<h4>By Car</h4>
<p>Queen of Apostles is about 24 km (15 miles) west of Toronto, between the Queen Elizabeth Way (QEW) and Dundas St.</p>
<ul>
    <li>From the QEW: Take Mississauga Road north for about 2.5 km and turn right onto Doulton Drive. Go one block, then turn left at Blythe Road. Turn into the second driveway on your right.</li>
    <li>From Hwy. 401: Exit at Erin Mills Pkwy., go south, then turn left at Dundas St. and right at Mississauga Rd. Go to Doulton Drive, turn left, and then left again at the first intersection.</li>
</ul>

<h4>By Air</h4>
<p>From Toronto Pearson International Airport, follow Hwy. 427 South to the Queen Elizabeth Way (QEW), then go west to the Mississauga Road exit and follow the car directions above. The airport is 24 km (15 miles) from the Centre.</p>
